<dl id="n25076e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n25" href="#n25076e">N25 (VI.B.15)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n25all.htm#n25076e"> 76(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Benjamin / son of R Hand</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">So Rachel, dying in childbed, calls the babe Ben-oni, &lsquo;son of sorrow,&rsquo; but the father changes his name to <mark>Ben-jamin, &lsquo;son of the right hand.&rsquo;</mark> <small> Edward Clodd, <a name="ECTTT" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#ECTTT"><cite title="source">Tom Tit Tot</cite></a> (1898) 102</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c14045c" href="c14all.htm#c14045c">VI.C.14:045(c)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
